S.FORM: I 1966 a miheca saka 6 folad saka 15 a romi'ad masofoc ci Raimonds V jonis, malamikomoday a tamdaw. O Sawara'an no kitakit no Latvia anini i ci Raimonds V jonis, patirengan a romi'ad i 2015 a miheca saka 7 folad saka 8 a romi'ad.
